## Validation Checklist

Before submitting MCP response to harness:

✅ Response contains valid JSON
✅ Has required `task_id` field
✅ Has `chunk_results` or equivalent (varies by tool)
✅ All items have `knowledge_item_id`, `title`, `summary`
✅ For merge responses: all 7 buckets present (even if empty)
✅ No extra unknown fields that conflict with schema

